# Exploration: od

## Rounds
  round 0: 93 isolated cumulative, 121 identical in round (discovery)
  round 1: 122 isolated cumulative, 25 identical in round (refinement)
  round 2: 122 isolated cumulative, 46 identical in round (refinement)

## Observed: 16/21 flags
  14 solo, 2 via combination
  3 additional error-differentiated
  1 behavioral aliases detected
  2 indistinguishable under tested conditions

Aliases: -A = --address-radix, -N = --read-bytes, -j = --skip-bytes, -t = --format, -v = --output-duplicates

